00:00:47,580 --> 00:00:49,110
right in the middle of the subway exit.

5
00:00:49,140 --> 00:00:51,780
People found it strange and reported
it to the police. Go check it.

6
00:00:53,880 --> 00:00:54,840
Evacuate the crowd.

7
00:00:54,920 --> 00:00:56,740
Get the bomb squad in position
for inspection.

8
00:00:56,800 --> 00:00:58,030
Scatter, people!

9
00:00:58,039 --> 00:00:59,640
Scatter now! Move along!

10
